{"tid":109611,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"FBI 極秘「iPhone 破解工具」被偷！黑客公開放上網","createTime":"2017-02-06T05:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T11:25:43.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"18e9b6186cb0eede6318c46b91d656228cd284a4","tid":109611,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.price.com.hk/space/news/images/20170206/61a3da9b03e502297d7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.price.com.hk%2Fspace%2Fnews%2Fimages%2F20170206%2F61a3da9b03e502297d7f.jpg&h=34755fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1小時前 &bull; 最新情報<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去年 FBI 要求 Apple 幫忙破解一部曾經由恐怖份子擁有的 iPhone 5c，更加想 Apple 特別在 iOS 做一個「後門」，方便 FBI 日後的情報工作。被 Apple 堅決拒絕後，FBI 轉移向以色列的一間流動裝置保安公司 Cellebrite 尋求幫助。想不到這間保安公司最近被駭，令重要的工具曝光。<br />\n<br />\n一班匿名黑客之前成功入侵 Cellebrite 其中一個伺服器，取得大量重要內容。其中一個重大發現正是 FBI 使用的 iPhone 入侵工具，名為 UFED。現在黑客將 UFED 的部分程式碼公開，顯示這個工具能破解較舊的 iPhone (包括 iPhone 5c) 和 Android 及 BlackBerry 手機。"},{"pid":"883a3374fecb0800e7729681bddcf586b49e3ac1","tid":109611,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:01:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d95cecfc6e6e58000e446c8793296f57826702e","tid":109611,"uid":38203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:03:13.000Z","msg":"Watch dog 2"},{"pid":"718cecdf51dde290bca93a0e95a94a377e0c4e29","tid":109611,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:05:11.000Z","msg":"FBI 轉移向以色列的一間流動裝置保安公司 Cellebrite 尋求幫助。想不到這間保安公司最近被駭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51558f703e7617fab5612f366fca99b6a1facc54","tid":109611,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:09:50.000Z","msg":"黑客並未有將整個破解工具公開，因為此舉只是想證明他們有得到那個工具，作為向 FBI 的一個警告：只要有破解工具存在，就一定會流出，不會只有 FBI 自己用到。這就是 Apple 和 Tim Cook 堅決不肯製作「後門」的原因，因為漏洞很快會被無數黑客使用，包括世界各個毫不顧忌監控所有人的政權。只終受害者未必是恐怖份子，而是普羅大眾。"},{"pid":"e26eb3d4789a43bd613fe71e61da9523b6b64b68","tid":109611,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:09:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f21c1e534ddc65c46db215f79b34c05af55e3961","tid":109611,"uid":10011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:11:36.000Z","msg":"Watch Dog 3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f17b0d2342f5b82d698058250a7a6539b247f61","tid":109611,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:25:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>顯示這個工具能破解較舊的 iPhone (包括 iPhone 5c) 和 Android 及 BlackBerry 手機<br />\n一視同仁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇WP電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> windows phone 好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d4e45a9a341a59e229ea98bb1f607546f0499e","tid":109611,"uid":45256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:03:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>顯示這個工具能破解較舊的 iPhone (包括 iPhone 5c) 和 Android 及 BlackBerry 手機<br />\n一視同仁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇WP電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> windows phone 好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好條撚波，冇人用廢鳩事hack 咋卦？"},{"pid":"839d598578839d41219b47ed1724ea6c628754e6","tid":109611,"uid":48330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:10:11.000Z","msg":"watch dogs<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5120b7628b3a01270df2136d9ece05e670397ea","tid":109611,"uid":2470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:38: